<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbcbc227d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s4278"><num value="4278">§ 4278.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out the provisions of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbcbc227e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/86/380/s8">Pub. L. 86–380, § 8</ref>, <date date="1959-09-24">Sept. 24, 1959</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/73/706">73 Stat. 706</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
